title: Saves the Day - Stay What You Are
description:
Stay What You Are is the third album release from Princeton, New Jersey based band Saves the Day. The album spawned singles and videos out of the songs "At Your Funeral" and "Freakish". At the time of the recording, Saves The Day consisted of Chris Conley, Dave Soloway, Ted Alexander, Eben D&#039;Amico, and Bryan Newman.

   9. "All I&#039;m Losing is Me" 3:22
